[RUST-PROJ-R012] Warning: Build-time harness gate is incomplete
@ $TEMP/build.rs:1:1
fix: add the harness to [build-dependencies] and call rust_lang_project_harness::assert_rust_project_harness_build_clean_from_env_with_config(...) from build.rs
